            bindings = <
          &kp GRAVE  &trans     &kp UP    &trans     &kp RA(NUMBER_9)         &kp RA(NUMBER_0)           &kp LS(NUMBER_7)  &kp LS(NUMBER_8)  &kp LS(NUMBER_9)  &kp EQUAL
          &trans     &kp LEFT   &kp DOWN  &kp RIGHT  &kp RIGHT_PARENTHESIS    &kp RA(RIGHT_PARENTHESIS)  &kp LS(NUMBER_4)  &kp LS(NUMBER_5)  &kp LS(NUMBER_6)  &kp MINUS
&kp CAPS  &trans     &kp PG_UP  &trans    &kp PG_DN  &kp LEFT_BRACKET         &kp RPAR                   &kp LS(NUMBER_1)  &kp LS(NUMBER_2)  &kp LS(NUMBER_3)  &kp KP_MULTIPLY  &kp PLUS
                                &trans    &trans     &trans                   &kp PERIOD                 &kp LS(NUMBER_0)  &kp KP_COMMA
            >;
        };

        // ▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄

